      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2011 BMW M3 (E92) is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 delivering 414 hp to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The powertrain features eight individual throttle bodies and a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This example is mechanically robust, with documented rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing adjustable compression and rebound to suit both spirited canyon carving and daily transit. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the vehicle maintains excellent structural integrity and a visceral induction note that defines the peak of BMW M engineering.",
