      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis has been properly maintained, including a critical rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed cooling system. Power is managed through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional corner-exit traction. The suspension retains its precise factory geometry with upgraded polyurethane bushings for enhanced steering response. While the aesthetic shows minor signs of road-going use, the drivetrain and structural integrity remain excellent, making this a perfect candidate for the purist driver looking for peak E46 performance.",
